</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0462-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0462-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>Trumbull presented GWs letter to his council of safety on 6 December. Trumbull and the council denounced the Connecticut soldiers who had tried to leave the army as deserters but doubted their power to act upon the subject, and therefore referred it to the next General Assembly (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Royal R. Hinman, comp. &lt;i&gt;A Historical Collection, from Official Records, Files &amp;amp;c., of the Part Sustained by Connecticut, during the War of the Revolution&lt;/i&gt;. Hartford, 1842. ]">Hinman, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Historical Collection</span></span>, 338).</p>

